original: Once upon a time, in the celestial realms, there was an extraordinary being named Gary. He was not an angel or a deity, but rather God's personal assistant. God had entrusted Gary with the responsibility of answering prayers, granting miracles, and overseeing the mortal realm. Gary possessed immense power and total autonomy in carrying out his duties. From the humblest pleas to the most desperate
